  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your solar core is under attack by an alien invasion. Can you protect the core and save the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a spaceship with unique stats and weapons to combat the alien invaders. Fend off endless waves of alien crafts that grow stronger and stronger. To survive, you will need to adapt and upgrade both your spaceship and solar core. Seek out alien motherships and destroy them to slow down the invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from over 60 upgrades to enhance your ship. Choose wisely to create powerful builds that can repel the invasion. Each round offers the possibility to discover new synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your core to boost its survival chances. Lasers, rockets, and shields are at your disposal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Counterattack the alien motherships to destroy the aliens' spawn points, relieving pressure from your core. If you don't face the motherships, the motherships will come closer and closer. Time your counterattack carefully, as your core will be defenseless during that time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a spaceship with unique weaponry and stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full version offers over 60 upgrades to choose from, allowing for countless builds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your solar core and survive waves lasting from 30 to 90 seconds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast runs (under 30 minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect space junk to buy new upgrades and repair your core</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your solar core is under attack by an alien invasion. Can you protect the core and save the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a spaceship with unique stats and weapons to combat the alien invaders. Fend off endless waves of alien crafts that grow stronger and stronger. To survive, you will need to adapt and upgrade both your spaceship and solar core. Seek out alien motherships and destroy them to slow down the invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/30014054560f120c7d3ec1839b3668ef.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from over 60 upgrades to enhance your ship. Choose wisely to create powerful builds that can repel the invasion. Each round offers the possibility to discover new synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/5a9d551690ceb19171cd843e2587cb2b.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your core to boost its survival chances. Lasers, rockets, and shields are at your disposal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/b82861265bc1e5a29bf8e698d64d9f68.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Counterattack the alien motherships to destroy the aliens' spawn points, relieving pressure from your core. If you don't face the motherships, the motherships will come closer and closer. Time your counterattack carefully, as your core will be defenseless during that time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.poster.avif?t=1737576410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.webm?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113390/extras/a836064571df7b179374ccdaf1b4c210.mp4?t=1737576410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a spaceship with unique weaponry and stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full version offers over 60 upgrades to choose from, allowing for countless builds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your solar core and survive waves lasting from 30 to 90 seconds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast runs (under 30 minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect space junk to buy new upgrades and repair your core</p></li></ul>",
